        audit functionality altogether.

        This field is a member of `oneof`_ ``_audit_interval_seconds``.
    exemptable_namespaces (MutableSequence[str]):
        The set of namespaces that are excluded from
        Policy Controller checks. Namespaces do not need
        to currently exist on the cluster.
    referential_rules_enabled (bool):
        Enables

enabled.description: Enables the installation of Policy Controller. If false, the rest of PolicyController fields take no effect.

template_library_installed.description: Installs the default template library along with Policy Controller.  This field is a member of `oneof`_ ``_template_library_installed``.

audit_interval_seconds.description: Sets the interval for Policy Controller Audit Scans (in seconds). When set to 0, this disables audit functionality altogether.  This field is a member of `oneof`_ ``_audit_interval_seconds``.

exemptable_namespaces.description: The set of namespaces that are excluded from Policy Controller checks. Namespaces do not need to currently exist on the cluster.

referential_rules_enabled.description: Enables the ability to use Constraint Templates that reference to objects other than the object currently being evaluated.

log_denies_enabled.description: Logs all denies and dry run failures.
